title: Stephanie Farmer
text: Hi! I’m Steph, a third-year Ecosystem Science and Sustainability student at Colorado State University. I’m passionate about integrating sustainability into industries to create a more resilient future. Outside of academics, you’ll find me exploring the outdoors—whether it’s hiking, camping, or simply appreciating nature. I’m always eager to learn, connect, and make a positive impact!

title: CSU Projects
text:
In the Spring of 2025 I took a Quantitative Reasoning for Ecosystem Science based in R. I learned and wrote code with interesting data science.


What I learned in this assignment:

Created a Quarto Website
Learned how to format with styles
Customizing the navbar with quarto.yml
Finally figured out directories
